#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Simplified MongoDB with Panache"
msgstr "简明而充满魅力的 MongoDB"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "MongoDB is a well known NoSQL Database that is widely used, but using its raw API can be cumbersome as you need to express your entities and your queries as a MongoDB link:{mongodb-doc-root-url}/fundamentals/data-formats/documents/#document[`Document`]."
msgstr "MongoDB 是一款广为人知的 NoSQL 数据库，应用广泛，但直接使用其原生 API 可能会比较繁琐，因为你需要将实体和查询以 MongoDB link:{mongodb-doc-root-url}/fundamentals/data-formats/documents/#document[文档] 的形式进行表达。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "MongoDB with Panache provides active record style entities (and repositories) like you have in xref:hibernate-orm-panache.adoc[Hibernate ORM with Panache] and focuses on making your entities trivial and fun to write in Quarkus."
msgstr "MongoDB with Panache 提供了类似于在 xref:hibernate-orm-panache.adoc[Hibernate ORM with Panache] 中所使用的 Active Record 风格的实体（及存储库），并致力于让开发者在 Quarkus 中编写实体变得简单且充满乐趣。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is built on top of the xref:mongodb.adoc[MongoDB Client] extension."
msgstr "它是基于 xref:mongodb.adoc[MongoDB 客户端] 扩展构建的。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "First: an example"
msgstr "首先：一个例子"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Panache allows you to write your MongoDB entities like this:"
msgstr "使用 Panache，您可以像这样编写 MongoDB 实体："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You have noticed how much more compact and readable the code is compared to using the MongoDB API?\n"
"Does this look interesting? Read on!"
msgstr "你是否注意到，与使用 MongoDB API 相比，这段代码要简洁得多，也更易于阅读？这看起来很有意思吗？请继续阅读！"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"the `list()` method might be surprising at first. It takes fragments of PanacheQL queries (subset of JPQL) and contextualizes the rest.\n"
"That makes for very concise but yet readable code.\n"
"MongoDB native queries are also supported."
msgstr "`list()` 方法起初可能会让人感到意外。它接受 PanacheQL 查询片段（JPQL 的子集），并为其余部分提供上下文。这使得代码既简洁又易于阅读。此外，还支持 MongoDB 原生查询。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"what was described above is essentially the link:https://www.martinfowler.com/eaaCatalog/activeRecord.html[active record pattern], sometimes just called the entity pattern.\n"
"MongoDB with Panache also allows for the use of the more classical link:https://martinfowler.com/eaaCatalog/repository.html[repository pattern] via `PanacheMongoRepository`."
msgstr "上文所述的内容本质上就是 link:https://www.martinfowler.com/eaaCatalog/activeRecord.html[“活动记录”模式] ，有时也简称为“实体”模式。使用 Panache 的 MongoDB 还允许通过 `PanacheMongoRepository` 采用更经典的 link:https://martinfowler.com/eaaCatalog/repository.html[“存储库”模式] 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Solution"
msgstr "解决方案"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We recommend that you follow the instructions in the next sections and create the application step by step.\n"
"However, you can go right to the completed example."
msgstr "我们建议您按照后续各节中的说明，一步一步地创建该应用程序。不过，您也可以直接查看已完成的示例。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Clone the Git repository: `git clone {quickstarts-clone-url}`, or download an {quickstarts-archive-url}[archive]."
msgstr "克隆 Git 仓库： `git clone {quickstarts-clone-url}` ，或下载 {quickstarts-archive-url}[存档]。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The solution is located in the `mongodb-panache-quickstart` link:{quickstarts-tree-url}/mongodb-panache-quickstart[directory]."
msgstr "该解决方案位于 `mongodb-panache-quickstart` link:{quickstarts-tree-url}/mongodb-panache-quickstart[目录] 中。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
