#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Every query operation accepts passing parameters by index (`Object...`), or by name (`Map<String,Object>`)."
msgstr "每个查询操作都支持按索引（ `Object…​` ）或按名称（ `Map<String,Object>` ）传递参数。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When you use query parameters, be careful that PanacheQL queries will refer to the Object parameters name but native queries will refer to MongoDB field names."
msgstr "使用查询参数时，请注意：PanacheQL 查询将引用对象参数的名称，而原生查询则会引用 MongoDB 字段的名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
